考利久期<span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>D</mi><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>c</mi></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D_{mac}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.1514em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">ma</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">c</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.15em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>：</p>\n<p><span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>D</mi><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>c</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>T</mi></msubsup><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>T</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>×</mo><mi>C</mi><msub><mi>F</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>Y</mi><mi>T</mi><mi>M</mi><msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mi>i</mi></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>V</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">D_{mac}=\\sum_{i=1}^T \\frac{T_i \\times CF_i}{(1+YTM)^i}\\times \\frac{1}{{PV}}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true